Title: The Last Song (Musical)
Author: Example Production
Draft date: April 2026
Format: Secuens v0.9

===

ACT ONE

INT. THEATRE STAGE - NIGHT

The stage is dark. A single spotlight finds the center.

[[LX (cue 1) [fade=0s, preset=house_out]: House lights out]]

[[MQ (cue 2) [file="overture.wav", level=-6dB, fade=2s]: Overture begins]]

Audience settles. The music builds.

LX (cue 3) [fade=5s, preset=opening_wash]: Stage lights up — warm amber wash

The company assembles on stage.

AUTO (cue 4) [warn=2m, duration=15s]: Revolve stage — bring on set piece

COMPANY
(singing)
The curtain rises on a brand new day...

MQ (cue 5) with conductor downbeat: Orchestra swells — verse 1

[[SPOT (cue 6) [target=spot_1, level=80%]: Spot on LEAD — center stage]]
[[SPOT (cue 7) [target=spot_2, level=60%]: Fill spot on company — upstage]]

LEAD
(singing)
This is the moment I've been waiting for...

LX (cue 8) on "moment" [fade=1s, preset=lead_special]: Special on LEAD tightens

MQ (cue 9) with verse end: Transition to chorus

FLY (cue 10) [warn=1m, duration=8s]: Fly in backdrop — city skyline

The backdrop descends behind the company.

COMPANY
(singing — chorus)
One city, one dream, one night...

LX (cue 11) [fade=2s, preset=full_wash_cool]: Full stage — cool blue wash

SQ (cue 12) [file="rain.wav", level=-12dB]: Rain sound effect under music

MQ (cue 13) with chorus end: Bridge — strings only

The company breaks into choreography.

LX (cue 14) [duration=4s, preset=strobe_slow]: Slow strobe — 2 per second

AUTO (cue 15) [warn=30s, duration=6s]: Platform rises — LEAD elevated

LEAD
(speaking)
And this is where it ends.

LX (cue 16) [fade=3s, preset=single_follow]: Follow spot holds on LEAD

MQ (cue 17) with "ends": Music stops — silence

Beat.

SQ (cue 18) [file="thunder_distant.wav", level=-18dB, prewait=2s]: Distant thunder

MQ (cue 19) [prewait=1s, fade=4s, file="reprise.wav"]: Reprise — piano solo

LEAD
(singing — reprise)
But every ending is a beginning...

LX (cue 20) [fade=8s, warn=30s, preset=blackout]: Fade to blackout — slow

[[SPOT (cue 21) [fade=5s]: Spot fades last]]

MQ (cue 22) [fade=6s]: Music fades under

BLACKOUT.

END OF ACT ONE
